name: Harley 100 year anniversary commemorative knock-off t-shirt
description:
Harley orange on black.  This t-shirt featuring the Peg Leg Monkey ditching his hog mid-air celebrates Harley Davidson's 100 year anniversarry.  It was goning to make me rich.  Nuevo riche.  

It does not contain any of the following:
Harley logo, wolf, eagle, actual patented Harley specific bike, realistic renderings of famous Milwaukee locals.

It does contain:
The Peg Leg Monkey, 50's era motorcycle, Milwaukee Public Library, central branch, Harley Water Tower, and something else.

Get it now!  Cheap!

name: Hard, All over the Floor, A Bachelor's Guide to Living
description:
9X13 inches with 2 inch border
4 color hand pulled serigraph
pink, teal,  light green, black on
beige rag paper

signed and numbered by the artist

Combining dance schematics, vintage living room design, and karate, this image captures the life of a bachelor.  A found poem composed with rearranged text from vintage advertizing, explains, in words.  But, how can you really capture manhood with words?

Skrauss gave it a shot:

"Coolness of green sharpened with black
a hard dusting sharpens
A room should be easy to clean.
design an allover scheme.  easy to clean
start with a foot

hard allover the room.

In this scheme below
that will not show    marks
a handsome foot
can set your decorating scheme
hard allover the room."
